document_data.name: Fish Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Fish Street''' was a small road located in the city of [[Zhentil Keep]] during the midâ€“14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Location: Fish Street was located in Zhentil Keep's [[Zhentil Keep/Common Quarter|Common Quarter]] in the southwestern corner of the city. Fish Street connected [[Nool Street]] in the east with [[Beggars' Way]] in the west.
document_data.Notable Locations: A [[Zhentarim]] warehouse was located along Fish Street.
